            Attendify is a smart attendance management system for modern businesses. Get GPS-based punch in/out, secure PIN clock-in, employee leave management, and detailed monthly reports — all in one platform.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="#login" class="btn-primary">Login to Attendify</a>
