    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Powerful features in <em>Attendify</em></h2>
    <p class="section-desc reveal">Attendify combines everything your HR team needs — GPS tracking, PIN punch, leave management, and reports — into one fast and reliable platform.</p>

    <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card reveal">
            <div class="feature-icon">📍</div>
            <h3>GPS Location Tracking</h3>
            <p>Every Attendify punch-in and punch-out captures the employee's exact GPS coordinates — logged automatically with every attendance record.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card reveal">
            <div class="feature-icon">🔐</div>
            <h3>PIN-Based Clock In</h3>
            <p>Employees use a secure 4-digit PIN to clock in on Attendify — no app download needed, works on any shared device.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card reveal">
            <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
            <h3>Monthly Attendance Reports</h3>
            <p>Attendify auto-generates detailed PDF attendance reports for any employee or time period — ready to print or share in one click.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card reveal">
            <div class="feature-icon">🏖️</div>
            <h3>Leave Management</h3>
            <p>Employees apply for leave directly through Attendify. Admins approve or reject with full visibility on leave balances and history.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card reveal">
            <div class="feature-icon">📱</div>
            <h3>Mobile Friendly</h3>
            <p>Attendify works seamlessly on phones, tablets, and desktops — fully responsive with no app installation required.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card reveal">
            <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
