</section>


<!-- ── HOW IT WORKS ───────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="steps-section" id="how-it-works">
    <div class="section-label reveal">Simple process</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">How <em>Attendify</em> works</h2>
    <p class="section-desc reveal">Getting started with Attendify takes less than 5 minutes.</p>

    <div class="steps-grid" style="margin-top:48px;">
        <div class="step-card reveal">
            <div class="step-num">1</div>
            <h4>Admin Sets Up</h4>
            <p>Admin logs into Attendify and sets up the team — adding employees, assigning PINs, and configuring attendance settings.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card reveal">
            <div class="step-num">2</div>
            <h4>Employees Register</h4>
            <p>Each employee gets a unique Attendify code and PIN to access the system and clock in from any device.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card reveal">
            <div class="step-num">3</div>
            <h4>Daily Punch In/Out</h4>
            <p>Employees enter their PIN on Attendify at the start and end of each day. GPS location is captured automatically.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card reveal">
            <div class="step-num">4</div>
